message.entry: Input A must be a real full matrix of type single or double.
With the ByRows option, inputs must be 2-D.
Input B must be a real full matrix of type single or double.
Inputs A and B must have the same number of columns.
With the ByRows option, the DataScale value must be a scalar or a vector with the same number of elements as columns in A.
Value for DataScale parameter must be a positive non-NaN numeric scalar or vector of type single or double.
Value for ByRows parameter must be a logical.
Value for OutputAllIndices parameter must be a logical.
Unknown option specified. See the help for a list of valid options.
Tolerance value TOL must be a real, full (non-sparse), positive numeric scalar of type single or double.
